- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses generating trojaned datasets and DL models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with deep learning models and their vulnerabilities. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a potential category as the paper uses the MNIST dataset, which is commonly used in computer vision tasks. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper introduces an open source software framework for generating trojaned DL models.
